&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Page flow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Itâ€™s important work; But itâ€™s also repetitive.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I didnâ€™t want another framework.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
I didnâ€™t want something that hides the code.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
I didnâ€™t want a system that forces design decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I wanted a clean starting point that I could fully edit.&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;h2&gt;


  From Open Source to a Larger Shadcn Library
